            The vision of Owerri Archdiocesan JDPC is to create a serene society that accommodates the diversity of humanity through developmental projects, justice and peace.
            <br />
            Its mission is to advance the well-being of human development through empowerment, research, training, entrepreneurship, advocacy and community mobilization without any form of discrimination through a judicious use of available resources of human development.
